Code of Conduct

Our Pledge

We, at McCafferyTech, are committed to creating a welcoming and inclusive environment for everyone. We pledge to treat each other with respect, to be considerate, and to foster a space free from discrimination or harassment.

Expected Behavior
	•	Be respectful, kind, and considerate to all participants.
	•	Use inclusive language and encourage diverse participation.
	•	Refrain from harassment, intimidation, or any discriminatory behavior.

Unacceptable Behavior
	•	Harassment, intimidation, or discrimination in any form.
	•	Disruptive or offensive behavior that targets or excludes others.

Reporting Guidelines

If you experience or witness unacceptable behavior, please report it to us at shaunmccaffery@gmail.com We will respond promptly and take action as needed.

Scope

This Code of Conduct applies to all interactions and spaces related to McCafferyTech—both online and offline.

Enforcement

We take violations seriously. If we see behavior that violates this Code, we may take actions like warnings, temporary bans, or expulsion from the community.

Contact

For any questions or concerns, contact us at shaunmccaffery@gmail.com or through the GitHub Issues page.
